e with solving real-world problems.</p>\n<p>Here is a snapshot of my technical skills!</p>"}}]},"jobs":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Computer Technician","company":"Texas Christian University","location":"on campus","range":"September 2022 - Present","url":"https://www.tcu.edu/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Flashing operating systems image on Computers;</li>\n<li>Troubleshooting hardware and software issues and repairing devices if necessary;</li>\n<li>Ensuring proper safety of sensitive data by managing hard drives, and destroying data if necessary;</li>\n<li>Executing company policies, procedures, and safety standards to ensure the proper cleanliness and safety of the office and equipments.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Software Developer Intern","company":"Youth Empowerment Foundation","location":"remote","range":"March 2021 - August 2021","url":"https://www.yefindia.org/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Developed the official app of the NGO using Flutter &#x26; Firebase, currently used by thousands of active users;</li>\n<li>Streamlined the database management by independently developing an admin panel;</li>\n<li>Ensured the safety of sensitive user data by writing a secure set of firebase security rules;</li>\n<li>Saved hundreds of dollars in Firebase bills by restructuring Firestore document model to ensure minimum document reads and writes;</li>\n<li>Youngest developer to have been awarded the Star-performer award from the CEO for exceptional performance.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Flutter and Firebase Developer","company":"Gorin Systems","location":"remote","range":"June 2021 - November 2021","url":"https://gorinsystems.com/"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Wrote new features for different client apps and enhanced User Interfaces of some client applications;</li>\n<li>Worked closely in a team of 4, participated in team meetings, brainstormed new ideas and implemented them;</li>\n<li>Used softwares like Jira and hubstaff to work efficienty the agile way, took ownership of tickets and found and fixed bugs in ongoing projects.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Business Research Intern","company":"Youth Club India","location":"remote","range":"September 2021 - October 2021","url":"https://www.instagram.com/youth.club.india/?hl=en"},"html":"<ul>\n<li>Worked in a team of 15 and conducted research on the different factors which help a company stand out from its competition.</li>\n<li>Analyzed data and identified key trends and insights to inform strategic decision-making</li>\n</ul>"}}]},"featured":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CoviCare","cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"tracedSVG":"data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='400'%20height='195'%20viewBox='0%200%20400%20195'%20preserveAspectRatio='none'%3e%3cpath%20d='M0%2098v97h401V0H0v98m291-85c-26%204-29%205-32%2010-2%205-2%20144%201%20149%202%205%206%207%2028%2010%2033%205%2036%206%2039%204%207-4%206%201%207-88%200-89%200-85-6-88-4-3-8-2-37%203m3%2019l-34%204v61l1%2062%2027%203%2034%204%206%201V27l-34%205m5%2043l-27%202h-9v6c0%204%200%205%202%206l30-1h29V75l-4-1-21%201m-37%2019l-1%2018c0%2018%200%2018%202%2018a1931%201931%200%200162%204l1-20V93h-32l-32%201'%20fill='%2364ffda'%20fill-rule='evenodd'/%3e%3c/svg%3e","aspectRatio":2.0588235294117645,"src":"/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/ea4ab/covicare.jpg","srcSet":"/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/477ba/covicare.jpg 175w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/06776/covicare.jpg 350w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/ea4ab/covicare.jpg 700w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/14041/covicare.jpg 832w","srcWebp":"/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/89afa/covicare.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/9fca7/covicare.webp 175w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/37a4e/covicare.webp 350w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853e18df2815f/89afa/covicare.webp 700w,\n/static/7cb35a7d1a3d021ca67853