mshahi/healthly","external":""},"html":"<p>A health and fitness app which has a lot of useful functionalities such as:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Helps in calculating BMI and tells if it's good or not.</li>\n<li>Helps in formulating a custom meal plan with desired calorie intake using Spoonacular API.</li>\n<li>Displays Covid-19 cases in the world with custom graph.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Edbuddy","tech":["Flutter","Firebase","Dart"],"github":"https://github.com/madhavamshahi/Edbuddy/tree/main/edbuddy","external":""},"html":"<p>A community-driven platform to find free school supplies(e.g books, notebooks, pens, etc) in your school/university.\nBased on the MVC design pattern.\nWorks like a social network to find other students in your school or university to study with.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Weatherly","tech":["Dart","Firebase","Openweather API","Flutter"],"github":"https://github.com/madhavamshahi/WeatherLy","external":""},"html":"<p>WeatherLy is a beautiful app which displays information about the current weather condition of a particular place in a intuitive way. It uses the OpenWeather API to fetch the weather details using the GPS.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Blackjack Game","tech":["pyhton"],"github":"https://github.com/madhavamshahi/blackjackGame","external":""},"html":"<p>Blackjack game you can play with the computer.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CoviCare","tech":["Flutter","Firebase","MVVM Design Pattern","Twitter API"],"github":"","external":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.app.cohelp.app"},"html":"<p>An app which helped in finding Covid-19 resources such as plasma donor availability in a hospital, oxygen cylinder, supplies, etc during the pandemic.\nUsed the Twitter API to fetch and sort data from Twitter, it has a search bar using which the users can easily find the resources they're looking for. Based on the MVVM design pattern.\nSaved 10+ lives in India, featured in two major newspapers. 500+ downloads without any marketing with an app store rating of 4.6/5.</p>"}},{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Up-synced","tech":["Dart","Firebase","Flutter"],"github":"","external":"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.app.upsynced.app"},"html":"<p>Helps in connecting and keeping in touch with the people you meet at events.\nWith just a one second QR code scan, it shares all your profiles (LinkedIn, Github, Twitter, etc) to the other person and vice versa.\nBased on the MVVM design pattern\nDesigned and developed the front-end using Flutter and Dart, and the backend using Firebase (NoSQL database).</p>"}}]},"contact":{"edges":[{"node":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Get In Touch","buttonText":"Mail Me"},"html":"<p>Feel free to drop an email if you have a question or just want to say hello, I'll try my best to get back to you!</p>"}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["3115057458"]}